      "id": "1777698482679",
      "type": "text",
      "content": "\n        \n        \n        \n        <h2>New Section</h2><p><font color=\"#2dabb4\">Start writing here...</font></p><h3 data-section-id=\"1kjz9kj\" data-start=\"83\" data-end=\"109\">Current Issues to Fix:</h3>\n<ul data-start=\"110\" data-end=\"297\">\n<li data-section-id=\"uc7is9\" data-start=\"110\" data-end=\"178\">\nChanges made in the builder are&nbsp;<a href=\"www.naveen.design\" target=\"_blank\">not reflecting in the preview.</a><a href=\"www.naveen.design\" target=\"_blank\">not reflecting in the preview.</a></li>\n<li data-section-id=\"ixqrej\" data-start=\"179\" data-end=\"249\">\nThe <strong data-start=\"185\" data-end=\"220\">preview is not&nbsp;<a href=\"www.gogole.com\" target=\"_blank\">working</a>&nbsp;properly</strong> after creating a case study.\n</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1bm4dpb\" data-start=\"250\" data-end=\"297\">\n<strong data-start=\"252\" data-end=\"281\">Images are not displaying</strong> in the preview.\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"299\" data-end=\"302\">\n<h3 data-section-id=\"ar0sy6\" data-start=\"304\" data-end=\"330\">Required Improvements:</h3>\n<h4 data-start=\"332\" data-end=\"352\">1. Preview Sync</h4>\n<ul data-start=\"353\" data-end=\"507\">\n<li data-section-id=\"m4hrnz\" data-start=\"353\" data-end=\"431\">\nEnsure all changes made in the builder <strong data-start=\"394\" data-end=\"430\">reflect instantly in the preview</strong>.\n</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"u6tsex\" data-start=\"432\" data-end=\"507\">\nThe preview should always display the <strong data-start=\"472\" data-end=\"506\">latest saved or edited content</strong>.\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 data-start=\"509\" data-end=\"530\">2. Media Support</h4>\n<ul data-start=\"531\" data-end=\"688\">\n<li data-section-id=\"tqwegz\" data-start=\"531\" data-end=\"610\">\nFix image rendering so that <strong data-start=\"561\" data-end=\"609\">uploaded images display correctly in preview</strong>.\n</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"12ehct8\" data-start=\"611\" data-end=\"688\">\nAllow adding:\n<ul data-start=\"629\" data-end=\"688\">\n<li data-section-id=\"16daud8\" data-start=\"629\" data-end=\"641\">\n<strong data-start=\"631\" data-end=\"641\">Images</strong>\n</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"bs4f3n\" data-start=\"644\" data-end=\"654\">\n<strong data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"654\">GIFs</strong>\n</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1vnhdli\" data-start=\"657\" data-end=\"688\">\nOther supported media formats\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 data-start=\"690\" data-end=\"726\">3. Text Formatting Enhancements</h4>\n<ul data-start=\"727\" data-end=\"841\">\n<li data-section-id=\"1bjlf5y\" data-start=\"727\" data-end=\"841\">\nAdd options to:\n<ul data-start=\"747\" data-end=\"841\">\n<li data-section-id=\"1113olq\" data-start=\"747\" data-end=\"770\">\n<strong data-start=\"749\" data-end=\"770\">Change text color</strong>\n</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1gsj8rw\" data-start=\"773\" data-end=\"793\">\n<strong data-start=\"775\" data-end=\"793\">Add hyperlinks</strong>\n</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"19f9f3n\" data-start=\"796\" data-end=\"841\">\nApply basic formatting (bold, italic, etc.)\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 data-start=\"843\" data-end=\"874\">4. Table of Contents (ToC)</h4>\n<ul data-start=\"875\" data-end=\"1114\">\n<li data-section-id=\"1kkn7gp\" data-start=\"875\" data-end=\"950\">\nIn the text section, provide an option to <strong data-start=\"919\" data-end=\"949\">enable “Table of Contents”</strong>.\n</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"10i0pxf\" data-start=\"951\" data-end=\"1024\">\nWhen enabled:\n<ul data-start=\"969\" data-end=\"1024\">\n<li data-section-id=\"sf1367\" data-start=\"969\" data-end=\"1024\">\nAdmin should be able to <strong data-start=\"995\" data-end=\"1023\">manually enter ToC items</strong>.\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1f9po88\" data-start=\"1025\" data-end=\"1114\">\nRestriction:\n<ul data-start=\"1042\" data-end=\"1114\">\n<li data-section-id=\"16fyow1\" data-start=\"1042\" data-end=\"1114\">\nOnly <strong data-start=\"1049\" data-end=\"1074\">one Table of Contents</strong> can be active per case study at a time.\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 data-start=\"1116\" data-end=\"1145\">5. Mobile Responsiveness</h4>\n<ul data-start=\"1146\" data-end=\"1342\">\n<li data-section-id=\"1vqdjn5\" data-start=\"1146\" data-end=\"1244\">\nThe entire experience (builder + preview + published case study) should be <strong data-start=\"1223\" data-end=\"1243\">fully responsive</strong>.\n</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"18qvuis\" data-start=\"1245\" data-end=\"1342\">\nEnsure proper layout and readability across:\n<ul data-start=\"1294\" data-end=\"1342\">\n<li data-section-id=\"8h4av7\" data-start=\"1294\" data-end=\"1310\">\nMobile devices\n</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1cm0ngx\" data-start=\"1313\" data-end=\"1322\">\nTablets\n</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1f6pz0l\" data-start=\"1325\" data-end=\"1342\">\nDesktop screens\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1344\" data-end=\"1347\">\n<h3 data-section-id=\"h4ahxw\" data-start=\"1349\" data-end=\"1369\">Key Requirement:</h3>\n<ul data-start=\"1370\" data-end=\"1533\">\n<li data-section-id=\"1n2ec0r\" data-start=\"1370\" data-end=\"1445\">\nEverything should work seamlessly:\n<ul data-start=\"1409\" data-end=\"1445\">\n<li data-section-id=\"w9963t\" data-start=\"1409\" data-end=\"1445\">\nBuilder → Save → Preview → Publish\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"khiaeo\" data-start=\"1446\" data-end=\"1533\">\nEnsure <strong data-start=\"1455\" data-end=\"1513\">no mismatch between builder content and preview output</strong> across all devices.</li></ul>\n      \n      \n      \n      ",
      "tocEntry": true,
      "tocName": "n builder"
    },
